HEADWORD: Wood-sere
<hw>Wood"-sere`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The time when
there no sap in the trees; the winter season.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>wood-seer</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Tusser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
